data.description: Fantastic move in ready 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home with room for everyone and no one to build behind you! Laminate wood flooring! Living room with fireplace & ceiling fan! Kitchen with granite countertops, tiled backsplash, breakfast bar, pantry, gas range, built in microwave, dishwasher & refrigerator stays! Dining room or could make great office space! Bedroom on main level with ceiling fan and nearby full bathroom! Owner suite with vaulted ceiling, fan, bathroom with double sink vanity, tile around soaking tub, separate shower, walk in closet & water closet! Spacious spare bedrooms! Bathroom with double sink vanity! Laundry room! Patio overlooking private backyard! Two car garage! Great location with easy access to shopping, restaurants & more!
